B.a_a={healthy:0,scab:1,"black rot":2,"cedar rust":3,"powdery mildew":4,"late blight":5,"early blight":6,"common rust":7,"gray leaf spot":8,"northern leaf blight":9,"leaf blight":10,"black measles":11,"bacterial spot":12,huanglongbing:13,"leaf mold":14,"septoria leaf spot":15,"spider mites":16,"target spot":17,"yellow leaf curl":18,"mosaic virus":19,"leaf scorch":20}
B.acM=new A.eR("Crop displays optimal structure. Maintain current watering and fertilizing cycles.","Maintain steady crop rotation intervals and perform regular soil pH testing.","Standard organic NPK compost (10-10-10) during active growth states.")
B.acN=new A.eR("Apply lime sulfur or captan fungicides. Rake and destroy fallen leaves.","Prune trees to keep the canopy open and allow leaves to dry quickly after rain.","Apply copper-based fungicides or sulfur sprays at 10-day intervals. Avoid heavy nitrogen.")
B.acX=new A.eR("Prune infected tissue. Apply copper fungicide. Ensure good air circulation.","Sanitize tools between cuts. Keep plants spaced appropriately.","Apply systemic fungicides during pre-bloom and post-bloom intervals.")
B.acW=new A.eR("Remove nearby juniper hosts. Apply fungicide during wet spells.","Plant rust-resistant cultivars and clean debris around orchards.","Use preventive sterol-inhibitor fungicides at tight cluster and petal fall stages.")
B.ad_=new A.eR("Apply sulfur or potassium bicarbonate. Improve air circulation. Avoid overhead watering.","Keep humidity low. Prune infected stems to improve sunlight penetration.","Apply organic neem oil or sulfur-based biological fungicides at weekly intervals.")
B.acO=new A.eR("Apply copper fungicides immediately. Prune lower infected leaves. Keep foliage dry.","Isolate crop beds from neighboring rows to mitigate fungal spore transfers.","Apply mancozeb or copper-based treatments. Avoid nitrogen-heavy fertilizers during outbreaks.")
B.acU=new A.eR("Apply chlorothalonil or copper fungicide. Mulch to reduce soil splash. Rotate crops.","Stake plants to keep leaves off the ground and water at the base only.","Incorporate potassium-rich organic fertilizers to build crop resistance.")
B.acQ=new A.eR("Apply sulfur or copper fungicides. Destroy infected crop residues post-harvest.","Use resistant hybrid seed varieties and rotate crops with non-grasses.","Foliar application of strobilurin-class fungicides under high-humidity conditions.")
B.acT=new A.eR("Rotate crops. Apply fungicide at first symptoms. Till under residue.","Avoid conservation tillage in fields with a history of leaf spot infections.","Apply triazole-based systemic fungicides during early vegetative stages.")
B.acV=new A.eR("Use resistant hybrids. Apply fungicide when lesions appear on lower leaves.","Manage residue decomposition through fall tillage and rotate crops.","Use strobilurin or triazole fungicides during tasseling and silking intervals.")
B.acL=new A.eR("Remove infected leaves. Apply copper-based fungicide. Avoid overhead irrigation.","Clean garden debris thoroughly before planting next season.","Apply copper fungicides or bio-fungicides to protect newly emerged leaves.")
B.ad2=new A.eR("Prune affected canes. Apply fungicide. Reduce stress with proper irrigation.","Protect pruning wounds with wound sealants to prevent fungal entry.","Apply liquid lime sulfur sprays during the dormant winter period.")
B.acJ=new A.eR("Apply copper spray. Remove infected leaves. Avoid working wet plants.","Use certified disease-free seeds and sanitize stakes/cages annually.","Use fixed copper sprays mixed with mancozeb to increase bactericidal efficacy.")
B.acI=new A.eR("Remove infected trees. Control psyllid vectors with insecticides. No cure available.","Use insect nets for nurseries and plant only certified disease-free rootstock.","Apply systemic insecticides (neonicotinoids) to control the Asian citrus psyllid.")
B.acY=new A.eR("Improve ventilation. Reduce humidity. Apply fungicide to lower leaves.","Maintain greenhouse temperature above 15\xb0C and ensure horizontal fans are active.","Apply preventive chlorothalonil or copper fungicides to prevent spore germination.")
B.acP=new A.eR("Apply fungicide. Remove lower infected leaves. Stake plants for airflow.","Apply straw or plastic mulch to prevent fungal spores from splashing onto foliage.","Use chlorothalonil or copper fungicides. Support crop with organic compost tea.")
B.ad0=new A.eR("Apply miticide or neem oil. Increase humidity. Introduce predatory mites.","Spray foliage with water to wash off dust and discourage mite nesting.","Apply insecticidal soap or neem oil. Avoid broad-spectrum insecticides that kill natural predators.")
B.acS=new A.eR("Apply fungicide. Avoid overhead irrigation. Improve air circulation.","Ensure crop spacing allows adequate sunlight to dry the lower canopy.","Apply chlorothalonil, mancozeb, or strobilurin-class fungicides.")
B.acR=new A.eR("Control whiteflies with insecticides. Use reflective mulch. Remove infected plants.","Install insect-proof screens (50-mesh) on greenhouse ventilation windows.","Use imidacloprid systemic drench during transplanting to suppress whitefly vectors.")
B.ad1=new A.eR("Remove infected plants. Control aphids. Disinfect tools. No chemical cure.","Remove weed hosts from borders and wash hands/tools with soap or milk solution.","No chemical cure. Spray mineral oils to reduce aphid transmission rates.")
B.acZ=new A.eR("Apply fungicide. Remove scorched leaves. Maintain consistent soil moisture.","Mulch plants to keep roots cool and water deeply during dry periods.","Apply potassium and organic fertilizers to help the crop recover from drought stress.")
